            "bio": [
                "As the Google Product Expert for Android, Manas has over 8+ year of experience building for the Android ecosystem. He has built over 30+ applications for the Android ecosystem and has won the WWDC20, the World Ocean Science Congress Competition for his applications. <a href=\"https: //www.deccanherald.com/specials/wwdc-2020-meet-indian-apple-swift-student-challenge-winners-850697.html\"><sup class=\"ml-1 mt-1 text-[#073042] font-medium\"> 1 </sup> </a> <sup class=\"text-[#073042]\">,</sup><a href=\"https://www.thehindu.com/sci-tech/technology/manas-malla-15-year-old-developer-from-visakhapatnam-on-his-app-ecofun-at-wwdc-2020-swift-student-winner-meet/article31914475.ece\"><sup class=\"ml-[2px] mt-1 text-[#073042] font-medium\">2</sup></a>",
                "With over 65+ badges on the Google Developer Profile, Manas has been the Android Study Jams Facilitator in the past for Google Developer Groups Vizag, where he has taught over 350+ enthusiastic developers on how to build for Android. <a href=\"https://gdg.community.dev/events/details/google-gdg-vizag-presents-android-study-jams-session-2/\"><sup class=\"ml-[2px] text-[#073042] mt-1 font-medium\"> 5 </sup> </a>",
                "<br /> He has been certified by The Cambridge Certification Authority with a whooping 99% in the Java Level 1-2 examinations when he was taking his Android Developer Program certification.<a href=\"https: //github.com/ManasMalla/MyAchievements/blob/master/CCA-Certificate-Java%20Level%201.pdf\"> <sup class=\"ml-1 mt-1 text-[#073042] font-medium\">3</sup></a> <sup class=\"text-[#073042]\">,</sup> <a href=\"https://github.com/ManasMalla/MyAchievements/blob/master/CCA-Certificate-Java%20Level%202.pdf\"> <sup class=\"ml-[2px] text-[#073042] mt-1 font-medium\"> 4 </sup></a>"
